QuestData.Title: Changing the Tide
QuestData.Description: It is time to retaliate against this foe. Meet me at Retribution Point and we will take this fight to the Shadow Council.$B$BTeron'gor shall not feast on another soul so long as we stand in his way! His reign of terror ends today.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Restalaan at Retribution Point.
QuestData.RewardText: Our enemy has been pushed back and Auchindoun's defenses restored thanks to your help, but we are not yet done here.
